#14516
zoomaster master~
the Zoomaster~
The Zoomaster stands here with a plastered smile greeting newcomers and casting sideways glances over his shoulder.
~
   This man's 6' 2" frame stands dressed in a dark blue coat with brass
buttons that reach all the way up to his burly neck.  He's wearing a dark
brown pant with the cuffs rolled up to reveal worn leather boots.  He looks as
if he is trying to emit an air of authority, but its apparent by his nervous
fidgeting and constant sideways glances that he's on the lookout for
something.  Underneath his eyes are bags that were clearly earned by sleepless
nights.  Many days of not shaving has earned his face a dirty looking scruff
that barely conceals his sharp facial features.  
~
