changing.  It appears to be a curious-natured creature as it's sometimes long
tentactles reach out to everything around it, probing and caressing.  It moves
in a slow manner as it examines, but always the tentacles pull back to its
main body.  The color seems to always return to a neutral gray, but flows from
grey to white to black in differnet hues.  The main body, if you could call it
that, is spherical in shape, but seems to have the pliability to be able to
change that as well.  
~
