#14531
nark~
the nark~
The nark scuttles about on its many legs emitting a hiss that sounds like razors scraping rock.
~
   This creature looks like a mash of several different venomous animals.  
Its body is armored with a glossy black carapace that stems all the way down
to its legs.  The legs themselves resemble spider legs that articulate at at
least three different joints until they end at razor sharp points.  This
creature seems to lack any discernable eyes, but responds quickly to any
noise.  Fine, sharp hairs cover each leg and look more like deadly pins that
could shoot out at any moment.  It scuttles about seeming to search for prey
and emits a hiss that sounds like razors scraping against stone.  
~
