#14532
Sinzhe~
Sinzhe~
The huge, dark Sinzhe stands here, observing everything with cold eyes.
~
Sinzhe stands six feet five, without an ounce of fat on him. All bone and
muscle, he moves like a cat, his slightest twitch pure liquid grace. He works
hard to stay hard but not to become overly muscled. He is very dark, but a
deep mahogany more than an ebony. He glows with conviction, an unshakable inner
strength. Gil-Glash recruited Sinzhe and his tribe, all superior warriors, as
a supplement to the Grey Slayers. Sinzhe leads the main garrison, rumors say
he was positions thus so Gil-Glash could keep him separated from Lady Volhm,
whom he often challenged to lengthy, destructive duels that always end in
draws. He can't fathom why his military genius isn't universally hailed.
~
